msg: Fixed problem where collections within transient objects where not being marked as transient, hence the contents of those collections where not serialized (copied from trunk).

author: rmatthews
msg: The execute client action method in distribution passed across the inserts, updates and deletes to the server in a different order to the one the where executed in during the execution of the action method .  This has now been fixed  so the order is consistent.
